<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: photosynthesis -->
  <VRE_Photosynthetic.label>光合作用</VRE_Photosynthetic.label>
  <!-- EN: This person is capable of converting light energy into chemical energy due to the special genetic composition of their skin. They do not become hungry if exposed to sunlight. -->
  <VRE_Photosynthetic.description>这个人的皮肤由特殊基因组成，能够将太阳能转化为化学能。如果他沐浴于阳光下，将不会感到饥饿。</VRE_Photosynthetic.description>
  <!-- EN: in sunlight -->
  <VRE_Photosynthetic.stages.in_sunlight.label>在阳光下</VRE_Photosynthetic.stages.in_sunlight.label>
  <!-- EN: out of sunlight -->
  <VRE_Photosynthetic.stages.out_of_sunlight.label>不在阳光下</VRE_Photosynthetic.stages.out_of_sunlight.label>
  
  <!-- EN: sap blood -->
  <VRE_SapBlood.label>粘稠血液</VRE_SapBlood.label>
  <!-- EN: This person has a thick, sticky, orange blood that greatly slows down their bleed out time, however it also impacts their ability to do work. -->
  <VRE_SapBlood.description>这个人有着又浓又粘的橙色血液，这大大减缓了他的出血时间，但同时也影响了他的工作能力。</VRE_SapBlood.description>
  
  <!-- EN: saplingchild needs planting -->
  <VRE_Saplingchild.label>婴苗需要种植</VRE_Saplingchild.label>
  <!-- EN: When a colonist with saplingbirth gene becomes pregnant, they need to designate a place to plant their offspring. If they don’t do it before the second trimester begins (6 days), the pregnancy will be terminated. -->
  <VRE_Saplingchild.description>当一个携带育苗基因的殖民者怀孕后，她需要指定一个地方来种植自己的后代。如果在妊娠中期开始前（6天）不这样做，妊娠将会被终止。</VRE_Saplingchild.description>
  
</LanguageData>